01:37:05.738 --> 01:37:08.782
Kunta Kinte.

01:37:08.866 --> 01:37:12.870
Son of Omoro Kinte.

01:37:15.039 --> 01:37:19.210
You live, Kunta Kinte.

01:37:21.045 --> 01:37:22.463
